This memorandum, issued by President Barack Obama on June 29, 2015, delegates authority to the Secretary of Defense to fulfill the certification requirement specified in section 1035 of the National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2013. The memorandum also states that any reference to section 1035 shall be considered applicable to any future provision that is the same or substantially the same provision. The Secretary of Defense is directed to publish this memorandum in the Federal Register.